	<key>readme</key>
	<string># Paste Formatted Date

Generate and paste today's date in various formats.

## Usage

* date             — list all formats
* date &lt;filter&gt;   — filter by format name or value (e.g. "ISO", "YYYY", "unix")

Select a result to copy and auto-paste the date.</string>
